node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Adam Calhoun on August 27, 2021. May be an image of standing.

node.text:
We have no President, our Country is running on auto pilot. Right now there are Americans dying by the hands of terrorists. Right now there should be nothing but rubble and dust in return. Send everybody and unleash the worlds deadliest military. Save the people that need saving and erase the existence of anyone that opposes us. We need somebody to lead our Country before we are only left with memories of what America used to be. With the upmost disrespect to our current administration. 
-Adam B. Calhoun-

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Adam Calhoun on August 26, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, beard and outdoors.

node.text:
How many of you have ran out of words to describe what’s going on in our Country? Nothing makes sense anymore and at this point, everything is misinformation. If they lie to us enough, most people will start to believe the lie. If they force us enough, most people will comply. We went from to 2 week’s to “flatten the curve” to forcing Americans to wear masks and take a shot. Men competing in women’s sports, teachers calling students by their “pronoun”, what’s happening in AFGHANISTAN!? All the craziness that is going on right now, is what happens when you give the weakest people the loudest voices. 
.
.
.
#crazy #times #sad #whatsnext #save #america

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by Adam Calhoun on August 18, 2021. May be an image of 1 person, beard and outdoors.

node.text:
Here we go... Please read
Put fear into the people. Only let one ideology be broadcasted on the television and all social platforms. If anyone speaks against this, censor them. Force unwanted things on the people and if they don’t comply, take their jobs. Take this shot, wear this mask, stay away from each other. Pump out misinformation and tell them it’s the truth. Tell the people who love this Country and are ashamed of what it’s become, that they are terrorists. Let the weak and those in fear believe they are in control. Silence the strong 
BY ANY MEANS NECESSARY. 
What’s all that sound like to you?
Our government and most of its politicians belong in the very prisons they built. I miss our Country.
.
.
.
#facts #america #fight #standup #freedom #preach #acal #adamcalhoun

node.text:
I’m glad to have him home for good. I’ve only had to punch him a few times. We’re backkkk! Who remembers those old funny videos we used to make? Well... We’ll be dropping new ones. 
DID YOU AMERICA TODAY.
.
.
.
#father #son #acal #america #parenting

node.text:
If you’re always real, you can’t lose. You can’t throw dirt on my name, I’ve been muddy. I will always show you guys my whole life. You guys have watched me become an older man. It’s an honor and privilege sharing my life with y’all. 
.

#live #life #muddy #mudding #mud #happy #smile #usa #acal #adamcalhoun

node.text:
This is what perseverance looks like. I could cry looking at this picture. We started in my brother’s basement with no bed, I had no car, no license. Here’s what I did have... I had a son whose life depended on me. I had a job and I had no quit in me. Just know, you’re never out of the fight. If you’re willing to stand, you’ll make it. Thank you all for changing mine and my sons life. 
.
.
.
#thankyou #love #life #father #son

node.text:
Shirt at @acal_apparel 
This is real life and this is happening. Official announcement coming by the end of this year. This is what by the people, for the people looks like. You want to talk about prison reform, I’ve been there. You want to talk blue collar, hard working Americans, I worked in the mills. I’ve been to the bottom of the barrel and I never gave up or made excuses. We live in a Country where you can make it as far as your grit will take you. You get me in front of these politicians and I’m gonna show them what a real American has to say. They can’t drag my name through the mud, I’ve been walking in it my whole life. I am a free man of The United States Of America and I’m about to show the world what we’re made of. 
.
.
.
#free #man #america #acal #adamcalhoun #usa #president
